417
00:29:23,300 --> 00:29:25,433
Tuanku adalah bijaksana, berakhlak mulia dan berwawasan.

418
00:29:27,300 --> 00:29:28,166
Kami mohon agar Engkau perkenankan kami

419
00:29:29,700 --> 00:29:30,533
