00:31:04,100 --> 00:31:06,233
Kami mohon agar dimakbulkan.

449
00:31:08,300 --> 00:31:09,433
Adakah anda tahu

450
00:31:11,300 --> 00:31:13,933
kenapa Maharaja juga digelar 'Gabenor Keluarga'?

451
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:19,533
Menteri Zhao memberitahu saya

452
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:23,933
bahawa dalam tempoh Tiga Kerajaan, Jiang Ji Wei,

453
00:31:24,233 --> 00:31:25,633
